# Final Work Reports

When reporting completed work, include a concise recommended next step so the project can keep moving.

- Summarize what changed and what was verified.
- Call out any remaining risks or blockers.
- End with a short "Recommended next step" that names the next concrete task.
- If the work followed a project plan document, reference the relevant plan or milestone.

